@node "Writing" " How to write an article to XtremeGames? "

<==========================================================================>
                       XtremeGames Writing Guidelines
<==========================================================================>

The four most important requirements for submissions to XtremeGames are:

     1.  Please use English. Finnish is also acceptable, but we prefer
         English, because I hate translating. :)

     2.  Please use paragraphs.  It's hard on the eyes to have solid screens
         of text.  If you don't know where to make a paragraph break, guess.

     3.  Please put a blank line in between paragraphs.  It makes formatting
         the magazine much easier.

     4.  Please send us your article in ASCII format.

Please stipulate as well if you wish to retain copyright or hand it over to
the editor.

@{"Kari Suvivaara" link "Editor1"}
