@node "Scions" " Reviewing Almagica - Scions of a Forgotten World V0.18 "

<============================================================================>
     @{b}Almagica - Scions of a Forgotten World V0.18@{ub}     By: @{"Kari Suvivaara" link "Editor1"}
<============================================================================>

DESCRIPTION

   Almagica - Scions of a Forgotten World V0.18 is a realtime fantasy war strategy game like WarCraft (PC) and WarCraft 2 (PC).

FEATURES

 - 5 levels.
 - 4 different troops and 4 different houses.
 - Unit experience.
 - Nice graphics and sound effects.
 - Dynamic screen size.
 - Support for Audio Cards (AHI audio system).
 - Supports CyberGraphiX, but it's quite primitive. (Didn't have an opportunity to test, though.)
 - Default actions.
 - Possibility to "paint" units like choosing many icons on WB!
 - Possibility to choose units with shift-button.
 - Keyboard shortcuts to easy the game.

REQUIREMENTS

AGA or CyberGraphiX, OS 3.0 or better, 4 MB memory, 68020 or better, about 1.2 MB HD space and AHI for the audio.

